ame as CSS class in the body tag. Any help on this would be appreciated. Thanks!\n</p><img src=\"http://feeds.feedburner.com/~r/W3TOTALCACHE/~4/eljHL5X9K7I\" height=\"1\" width=\"1\" /></p>\r\n<h4>\r\n	<a href=\"http://feedproxy.google.com/~r/W3TOTALCACHE/~3/9kNhZJQOE1c/plugin-w3-total-cache-upload-the-media-to-cdn\">Firkraag85 on &quot;Upload the Media to CDN&quot;</a>\r\n</h4>\r\n<p>\r\n	<p>Hi Frederick,</p>\n<p>Yesterday I discover W3 Total Cache were disabled at my site, I don\'t know my... If I turn it on, all the images that aren\'t at CDN doesn\'t display.</p>\n<p>If I pretend to did sync the files, all starts from 0, and syncing 90000*3 images, is a LOT... Could it be possible to select \"start from the last\" or something like that? I mean, last files modified first.</p>\n<p>Thanks again and again, you have created a great plugin.<br />\nJulio</p>\n<p><a rel=\"nofollow\" target=\"_blank\" href=\"http://wordpress.org/extend/plugins/w3-total-cache/\">http://wordpress.org/extend/plugins/w3-total-cache/</a>\n</p><img src=\"http://feeds.feedburner.com/~r/W3TOTALCACHE/~4/9kNhZJQOE1c\" height=\"1\" width=\"1\" /></p>\r\n<h4>\r\n	<a href=\"http://feedproxy.google.com/~r/W3TOTALCACHE/~3/bvpBB3czEC0/plugin-w3-total-cache-w3tc-javascript-caching-problem-since-33\">shirazdrum on &quot;W3TC Javascript caching problem since 3.3&quot;</a>\r\n</h4>\r\n<p>\r\n	<p>Since the 3.3, it seems that the W3TC is having trouble combining java-scripts as I get errors accessing the cached version of the site. </p>\n<p>One of the errors: Uncaught TypeError: Object [object Object] has no method \'datepicker\'</p>\n<p>This is not a conflict of different scripts to be clear.</p>\n<p>You can see the error on here <a rel=\"nofollow\" target=\"_blank\" href=\"http://dreamdare.org\">http://dreamdare.org</a>  (inspect element) For example you can try the back to top button and it should scroll but jumps at the moment. It also should hide until half page which doesn\'t either. </p>\n<p>When I uncheck the minify JavaScript, it goes back to normal.</p>\n<p><a rel=\"nofollow\" target=\"_blank\" href=\"http://wordpress.org/extend/plugins/w3-total-cache/\">http://wordpress.org/extend/plugins/w3-total-cache/</a>\n</p><img src=\"http://feeds.feedburner.com/~r/W3TOTALCACHE/~4/bvpBB3czEC0\" height=\"1\" width=\"1\" /></p>\r\n\r\n<p style=\"text-align: center;\">\r\n	<a href=\"http://feeds.feedburner.com/W3TOTALCACHE\" target=\"_blank\">View Feed</a>\r\n</p>\r\n','no'),(1241,0,'_site_transient_timeout_browser_682391f34becba21cc36efdf29550e93','1324484883','yes'),(1242,0,'_site_transient_browser_682391f34becba21cc36efdf29550e93','a:9:{s:8:\"platform\";s:7:\"Windows\";s:4:\"name\";s:7:\"Firefox\";s:7:\"version\";s:3:\"9.0\";s:10:\"update_url\";s:23:\"http://www.firefox.com/\";s:7:\"img_src\";s:50:\"http://s.wordpress.org/images/browsers/firefox.png\";s:11:\"img_src_ssl\";s:49:\"https://wordpress.org/images/browsers/firefox.png\";s:15:\"current_version\";s:1:\"6\";s:7:\"upgrade\";b:0;s:8:\"insecure\";b:0;}','yes'),(1286,0,'_site_transient_timeout_browser_61d818edf8ac749898d2da4aa39552c0','1324486704','yes'),(1287,0,'_site_transient_browser_61d818edf8ac749898d2da4aa39552c0','a:9:{s:8:\"platform\";s:7:\"Windows\";s:4:\"name\";s:7:\"Firefox\";s:7:\"version\";s:5:\"8.0.1\";s:10:\"update_url\";s:23:\"http://www.firefox.com/\";s:7:\"img_src\";s:50:\"http://s.wordpress.org/images/browsers/firefox.png\";s:11:\"img_src_ssl\";s:49:\"https://wordpress.org/images/browsers/firefox.png\";s:15:\"current_version\";s:1:\"6\";s:7:\"upgrade\";b:0;s:8:\"insecure\";b:0;}','yes'),(1309,0,'initial_db_version','18226','yes'),(1310,0,'db_upgraded','','yes'),(1313,0,'_site_transient_timeout_browser_5dfcc60340cf2f486993c38488531d2c','1325697976','yes'),(1314,0,'_site_transient_browser_5dfcc60340cf2f486993c38488531d2c','a:9:{s:8:\"platform\";s:7:\"Windows\";s:4:\"name\";s:6:\"Chrome\";s:7:\"version\";s:11:\"17.0.963.12\";s:10:\"update_url\";s:28:\"http://www.google.com/chrome\";s:7:\"img_src\";s: